# Cursor-specific operating instructions
# Working with Cursor Agent (team workflow)

- Keep conversations short; start a new chat when switching features or the agent becomes confused.
- Always ask the agent to:
  1) restate the goal
  2) propose a plan
  3) implement in small steps
  4) add/update tests
  5) update docs
- Prefer referencing existing files instead of pasting long code into rules.
- When unsure about architecture, create an ADR in /docs/adr/ and keep it short.
